hex state machine diagram for the command mode

Character sets:
hexadecimal "h" [/]
address "a" [$,%,.]
mark "m" [']
command "c" [a,c,d,f,i,m,n,o,p,q,r,s,u,v,w,x,y,z]
name "n" [0-Z]
command separator "l" [|, lf, cr]

fields:
address 1
address 2
address 3
name
regex 1
regex 2
options

variables:
number of addresses
number of characters in name field
number of regular expressions


State 1:
aggregate an address
